## Creating virtual machine
## Installing debian
### Partitionning (for bonus)
Choose Manual
## Debian configuration
Switch user to root  
`su -`
Update and uprade apt  
`apt-get update -y`  
`apt-get upgrade -y`
#### Installing sudo 
`apt install sudo`  
Add user and create group sudo  
`usermod -aG sudo svogrig`
